{
    "identity": "nprot-7281",
    "title": "Beta-galactosidase activity assay for yeast",
    "content": [
        {
            "header": "Reagents",
            "content": "- Z Buffer: 60 mM Na2HPO4, 40 mM NaH2PO4\u00b7H2O, 10 mM KCl, 1 mM MgSO4, pH 7\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n- \u03b2-mercaptoethanol \\( 161-0710, Bio-Rad)\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n- Zymolyase-20T \\(120491, SEIKAGAKU CORPORATION)\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n- Protein Assay Dye Reagent Concentrate \\(500-0006, BIO-RAD) for Bradford Assay\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n- ONPG  \\(N1127, SIGMA ALDRICH)"
        },
        {
            "header": "Procedure",
            "content": "1. Collect approximately 5 \u00d7 107 cells from yeast exponentially growing cultures\r\n  \r\n\n\n 2. Pellet cells by centrifugation at 4000xg at 4\u00baC and wash once with water\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 3. Cells can be stored at -20\u00baC\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 4. Resuspend cells with 200 \u03bcl of Z Buffer + \u03b2-mercaptoethanol \\(0.27% \\(v/v)) containing 1mg/mL zymolyase-20T\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 5. Incubate samples 20-30 min at 30\u00baC to digest cells\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 6. Centrifuge cells at 13400xg for 5 min at 4\u00b0C\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 7. Transfer the supernatant to a new eppendorf\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 8. Use 1 or 2 \u03bcL of the extract to quantify the amount of protein using the Bradford assay \\(Concentration)\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 9. Mix 180 \u03bcl of extract \\(Volume) with 700 \u03bcL of Z Buffer + \u03b2-mercaptoethanol\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 10. Start the reaction by adding 200 \u03bcL of 4mg/mL ONPG \\(o-nitrophenyl- \u03b2-D-galactopiranoside\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 11. Incubate samples at 30\u00baC until they become yellow coloured \\(up to 90 minutes)\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 12. When yellow colour appears \\(Time), stop the reaction with 500 \u03bcL of Na2CO3 1M\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 13. Centrifuge cells at 13400xg for 1 min to pellet cells\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 14. Measure A460\r\n\n\n\r\n\n\n 15. \u03b2 -galactosidase activity is expressed in arbitrary units \\(U), from the following formula:\r\n\n\nU=\\(A460 x1000)/\\(Time \\(\u3016min) x Volume \\(\u00b5L)x Concentration \\(\u00b5g/\u00b5L)\u3017\u2061 )"
        }
    ],
